LocalizedName.description: Paw & Heart Animal Rescue - Animals in the Shelter and their Details

Description.description:
Paw & Heart is an animal rescue charity that operates animal shelters and liaises with local families to foster animals in need. The goal is to help every pet to get the veterinary care they need and to find their forever home.
The organization aims to: Improve record-keeping on animals staying at their shelters and foster homes Make it easier for first or adoption families to provide support Provide the social media team with insightful reports to help them encourage more people to foster or adopt a pet
